gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會每樣都試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望盡快趕走晒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2547da3a52ab5bc555b89a05af8101b42196fb","tid":908542,"uid":175732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"之前我都係屋企都好多蟻好煩<br />\n係自從成個夏天都開冷氣駁到冬天之後<br />\nd蟻見都見唔到"},{"pid":"f3a0caab0e56c9f367341263d4475a7e505dfb42","tid":908542,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"如果啲蟻係外來者入屋搵食 咁一定一條線咁一隻一隻走 <br />\n然後可以追索到個入口/源頭 例如窗口位<br />\n再封左佢就ok<br />\n<br />\nbtw大家用咩殺蟻<br />\n我會煲水 之後一野轟落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過之後要整番干<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"3f3c4186968b4d5f920f66b23a6eda5f38f2c239","tid":908542,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"講起蟻 尋日屋企前面啲泥地多左兩個蟻堆<br />\n見到啲泥谷起哂 一個個洞仔咁<br />\n就忍唔著手用熱水一野轟落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轟極都仲有 搞到我煲左幾轉水<br />\n<br />\n之後比啲仆街蟻咬撚左隻腳一野 仆哂佢地個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}